# Password Strength Checker 

## Description
A Python-based cybersecurity tool that evaluates password strength based on
industry-standard security rules.

## Features
- Length validation
- Uppercase & lowercase detection
- Numeric & special character checks
- Common password blacklist
- Strength rating (Weak / Medium / Strong)

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Regular Expressions (re module)

## Purpose
 This is a educational project to understand password security and brute-force resistance.

# For educational purposes only.
